Class AbstractInfoPack

java.lang.Object

public abstract class AbstractInfoPack
extends java.lang.Object
implements IInfoPack, java.lang.Iterable<AbstractInfoPack>

A base InfoPack class that acts as a node, for use with the provided implementation of Core.

Extend this to create new InfoPack types.
